ZH: 机场附近有很多酒店。
EN: There are many hotels near the airport.

ZH: 我们要去机场接我的朋友。
EN: We are going to the airport to pick up my friend.

ZH: 机场的安检非常严格。
EN: The security at the airport is very strict.

ZH: 我迷路了，不知道怎么去机场。
EN: I'm lost and don't know how to get to the airport.

ZH: 在机场我买了一本杂志。
EN: I bought a magazine at the airport.

ZH: 飞机飞行途中降落在机场。
EN: The plane landed at the airport during the flight.

ZH: 机场附近有很多出租车。
EN: There are many taxis near the airport.

ZH: 机场有很多商店和餐厅。
EN: There are many shops and restaurants at the airport.

ZH: 他们在机场等待了很长时间。
EN: They waited at the airport for a long time.

ZH: 机场的工作人员很有礼貌。
EN: The airport staff are very polite.

ZH: 我们找到了离机场不远的酒店。
EN: We found a hotel not far from the airport.

ZH: 在机场我买了一些特色小吃。
EN: I bought some local snacks at the airport.

ZH: 他们正在建设一个新的国际机场。
EN: They are building a new international airport.

ZH: 我的航班延误了，要在机场等待几个小时。
EN: My flight is delayed, so I have to wait at the airport for several hours.

ZH: 机场对残疾人友好设有专门的服务设施。
EN: The airport is disability-friendly and has special facilities for disabled people.

ZH: 我在机场遇到了一个老朋友。
EN: I ran into an old friend at the airport.

ZH: 我需要在机场取行李。
EN: I need to pick up my luggage at the airport.

ZH: 坐地铁去机场比打车便宜。
EN: Taking the subway to the airport is cheaper than taking a taxi.

ZH: 他们到机场送行，看着我们的飞机起飞。
EN: They went to the airport to see us off and watch our plane take off.

ZH: 我在机场等车的时候看了一本小说。
EN: I read a novel while waiting for my ride at the airport.
